{"tid":1828749,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"「饒舌之神」Eminem無預警強勢回歸！首波主打歌〈Darkness〉完整重現美國2017年槍擊案！","createTime":"2020-01-18T06:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T06:47:02.000Z","uid":34495,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1cca4147d0c808bc3973822e1bcd7347a4b7468","tid":1828749,"uid":34495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLri62J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLri62J.jpg&h=b92afe56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Rap God」Eminem阿姆突發宣告回歸！今天Eminem突然在Twitter發布收錄20首歌曲的最新專輯《Music To Be Murdered By》，專輯名稱很兇悍以外，專輯封面更是Eminem一手拿斧頭一手拿槍的畫面，完整致敬了知名驚悚片導演Alfred Hitchcock的原聲帶《Music To Be Murdered By》，除此之外，Eminem為這張專輯寫下的推文「It&rsquo;s your funeral.」更讓人期待專輯的內容！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38WvdHW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38WvdHW.jpg&h=63a23f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其Eminem上張以日本神風特攻隊為名的《Kamikaze》專輯Diss了一票當紅的饒舌歌手們，其中Machine Gun Kelly更是釋出〈Rap Devil〉的回擊歌曲，大膽挑戰「饒舌之神」引爆一番話題！不過此次Eminem似乎不打算先以Diss大戰作為開場，而是在歌曲中呼籲大眾關注社會議題，率先釋出的新歌〈Darkness〉MV拍出了2017年拉斯維加斯發生的槍擊案，以第一人稱的視角看了整起事件更讓人感到沈重，最後Eminem則以字幕呼籲人們為槍枝氾濫的議題發聲，勇於表達自己的意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LaiA9gJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLaiA9gJ.jpg&h=5b13dad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Music To Be Murdered By》的合作歌手陣容也相當精彩，有日前宣布暫時引退一陣子的紅髮艾德Ed Sheeran、去年底英年早逝的Juice WRLD和Anderson .Paak等等知名音樂人。目前整張專輯已經在各大音樂平台正式釋出，各位Eminem的信眾們可以立刻前往收聽了！<br />\n<br />\nSpotify:<br />\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/4otkd9As6YaxxEkIjXPiZ6?si=eNkB3esyQE-bN3m01EJa3Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Falbum%2F4otkd9As6YaxxEkIjXPiZ6%3Fsi%3DeNkB3esyQE-bN3m01EJa3Q&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=3959e932\" target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/album/4otkd9As6YaxxEkIjXPiZ6?si=eNkB3esyQE-bN3m01EJa3Q</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_knfDJFovKaSg9Um3nYVd2vin4XPQ7tOBo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DOLAK5uy_knfDJFovKaSg9Um3nYVd2vin4XPQ7tOBo&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=5583457c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_knfDJFovKaSg9Um3nYVd2vin4XPQ7tOBo</a><br />\n<br />\nApple Music:<br />\n<a href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/album/music-to-be-murdered-by/1495267282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmusic.apple.com%2Fus%2Falbum%2Fmusic-to-be-murdered-by%2F1495267282&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKKDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=d3f5a984\" target=\"_blank\">https://music.apple.com/us/album/music-to-be-murdered-by/1495267282</a>"},{"pid":"f8739256e6d5f032a7bd8a4277a641d4fbee2e1e","tid":1828749,"uid":34495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQ4gTLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQ4gTLz.jpg&h=346752bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NYNfYT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NYNfYT.jpg&h=33ea64fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DkYp2DV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkYp2DV.jpg&h=c75061ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"447ad0a1575d74ae8756bdee01640947f7c4584f","tid":1828749,"uid":17376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:29:04.000Z","msg":"Juicr wrld<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43aadbf7f4fd0fe01d6e46317a845eb2cbd3f2df","tid":1828749,"uid":34495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"仲未聽哂成隻Album 已經覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /